SUMMARY:Quest for Learning Spring 2026
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 50 years of Quest for Learning with our 99th season.\nWe meet for six Thursdays\, from April 9 to May 14 (9:30 till NOON) at\nHoly Trinity Lutheran Church\,\n31 South Duke Street\,\nLancaster\, Pennsylvania.\n\nThere will be lectures on areas related to science\, baseball\, health\, mortality\, reconnecting plus a half hour coffee and cookies break \n\n\n\n\n\n\n    Register Now
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/quest-for-learning-spring-2026/2026-04-16/
LOCATION:Trinity Lutheran Church\, 31 South Duke Street\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Education & Classes
ORGANIZER;CN="Quest":MAILTO:questlancaster@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
