SUMMARY:Complete History of America (Abridged) Opening Night
DESCRIPTION:Big Laughs. Live.\n\nFrom the pilgrims to pop culture\, this is American history like it’s never been told — fast\, fearless\, and hilarious.\n\nThree performers. Dozens of characters. A full-throttle joyride through the moments that made a nation and all the wild in between.\n\nSmart\, ridiculous\, and absurdly entertaining.\n\nAnything but a lecture\, this is a high-voltage comedy built for laughter\, connection\, and a night that’s anything but ordinary.\n\nNo textbooks. No tests. Just comedy in full swing. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n    Buy Tickets
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/complete-history-of-america-abridged-opening-night/
LOCATION:Prima Theatre\, 941 Wheatland Ave\, Lancaster\, 17603
CATEGORIES:Arts & Entertainment
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://fig.guide/content/uploads/sites/3/2026/01/25_CompleteHistory_1920x1080-1.avif
ORGANIZER;CN="Prima Theatre":MAILTO:info@primatheatre.org
END:VEVENT
