SUMMARY:Lancaster City Restaurant Week
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster City Restaurant Week takes place twice a year — in the Spring and Fall — spotlighting the chefs\, owners\, and staff who turn Lancaster into a destination for unforgettable food experiences. Managed by a small but dedicated team\, the event provides a free\, accessible platform for City of Lancaster restaurants to share their creativity\, flavors\, and stories with everyone who lives\, works\, or is drawn to visit our culinary community. \n\n\n\nExplore the specials\, deals\, and promotions by participating restaurants! \n\n\n\n\n    explore
