SUMMARY:16th Annual Forty Elephants Vintage & Handmade Spring Market
DESCRIPTION:Forty Elephants Vintage & Handmade Spring Market has 85+ curated vendors with everything for your vintage lifestyle. Vintage clothing & retro decor\, flea market finds\, quirky & vintage-vibe makers\, and food trucks. What a great way to shake off the winter blues\, and welcome warmer weather! See vendor list and previews on Facebook & Instagram. \nSunday\, April 19\, 2026\nDoubleTree Resort 2400 Willow Street Pike\, Lancaster\, Pa.\n10am-4pm Free Admission\nFood Truck: Brotherly Love Scratch Kitchen\nFree parking in the lot\, with handicap spaces available.\nRain or shine – we’re inside. \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Learn More
